features: 【Farmhouse Rustic Design】Transform your living spaces with this set of two table lamps, merging retro aesthetics with contemporary utility. Complemented by the soft elegance of linen fabric shades and the richness of an oil rubbed bronze lamp body and moire pattern glass, the combination of a nostalgic design exudes timeless sophistication. These farmhouse bedside desk lamps are more than just lighting; they are a statement piece, bridging classic appeal and modern functionality.

【3 Lighting modes】These table lamps for living room are designed to create the perfect atmosphere for any occasion. Their integrated LED night light (not changeable) and main light provide three adjustable lighting modes, allowing you to tailor your lighting to suit your mood. Whether you're unwinding after a long day or need focused illumination for work or reading, these rustic LED desk lamps deliver with style.

【Dual USB Charging Ports】Tired of hunting for available power outlets? These tall table lamps for bedroom come equipped with not one, but both 5V 2.1A USB-A & Type-C charging ports, ensuring your devices stay charged and your surfaces remain clutter-free. Experience the convenience of having power at your fingertips while enjoying the warm glow these lamps provide. It's a seamless blend of illumination and utility.

【Wide Application】These mid century table lamps aren't limited to one room; they're versatile companions for any space. Whether adorning your nightstands, accentuating your end tables, or illuminating your desk, they bring warmth and practicality. From creating cozy reading nooks to enhancing the style of your bedside tables, these desk lamps are essential elements of your home decor. Elevate your living spaces with these vintage table lamps, where form and function harmonize seamlessly.

【Perfect Large Size】These large table lamps strike the ideal balance between statement pieces and functional lighting. They are about 26 inch tall and their larger size adds a touch of grandeur to your room, while the E26 socket accommodates a variety of bulb types, offering you flexibility in choosing the right lighting intensity, from vibrant to subdued. If you encounter any problem during use, please feel free to contact us.
